sources.title: The Red Resurrection | Full Movie | Horror Thriller
sources.description:
The Red Resurrection - Fans of Resident Evil will love this film! Now 'resurrected' from a living death, a fearful and fractured young woman must overcome, not only the memories of what she was, but the monsters and men created by a deadly plague.
2017.  Stars: Rick Boling, Daniel Cutteridge, Trish Erickson-Martin
